            <div class="col-md-8">
              <h2 class="card-title mb-2">Welcome back, Admin! ðŸ‘‹</h2>
              <p class="card-text mb-0">Here's what's happening with your tourist business today.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 text-end">
